original_query: SELECT MIN(ph.Id) FROM postHistory as ph, posts as p, votes as v, users as u WHERE u.Id = p.OwnerUserId AND p.Id = ph.PostId AND p.Id = v.PostId AND ph.CreationDate>=CAST('2010-07-21 00:44:08' AS TIMESTAMP) AND p.ViewCount>=0 AND p.CommentCount>=0 AND v.VoteTypeId=2 AND u.Views>=0 AND u.Views<=34 AND u.UpVotes>=0
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT * FROM postHistory AS postHistory WHERE postHistory.CreationDate >= TIMESTAMP '2010-07-21 00:44:08'
CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT * FROM posts AS posts WHERE posts.ViewCount >= 0 AND posts.CommentCount >= 0
CREATE VIEW E4 AS SELECT * FROM users AS users WHERE CAST(users.Views AS INTEGER) >= 0 AND CAST(users.Views AS INTEGER) <= 34 AND users.UpVotes >= 0
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2E4 AS SELECT * FROM E2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4 WHERE E2.OwnerUserId=E4.Id)
CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT * FROM votes AS votes WHERE votes.VoteTypeId = 2
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2E4E3 AS SELECT * FROM E2E4 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3 WHERE E2E4.Id=E3.PostId)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1E2E4E3 AS SELECT MIN(Id) AS EXPR$0 FROM E1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2E4E3 WHERE E1.PostId=E2E4E3.Id)
